DRDGold’s Blyvoor Operation Accepts Offer of Help From Neighbour AngloGold

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-07-14T14:01:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-14/drdgold-s-blyvoor-operation-accepts-offer-of-help-from-neighbour-anglogold.html
DRDGold Ltd. (DRD)  said its “distressed
operating subsidiary,” Blyvooruitzicht Gold Mining Co., has
accepted an offer of assistance from  AngloGold Ashanti Ltd. (ANG) ,
Africa’s largest gold producer.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  